      "id": "PopularPost148743",
      "post_content": "Use with [Skyfire Kirin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skyfire Kirin) and [Cunning Bandit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cunning Bandit).  \n  \nAlso all the combos listed here. This is a pretty fun card in multiplayer too. You lose 1 card while taking several. The other combos listed here are pretty nice as well. This isn't a useless card. There are plenty of combos you can use this with.",
