      "id": "PopularPost215161",
      "post_content": "Fun card. Works great with the splice cards, as well as cards like [Act of Treason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason). Yes please, I'll take control of your [Darksteel Colossus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Colossus), bash you in the face with it, and then get rid of it altogether.  \n  \nIt's also a fun reset button. Say your opponent goes first, and sacs his [Polluted Delta](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Polluted Delta) to fetch his [Watery Grave](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Watery Grave) and plays it untapped to play a [Ponder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ponder). Play your [mountain](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mountain) and then this card. Sure, his library is a bit more organized, but he's down 3 life and a duel land.",
      "posted_by": "SirZapdos",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost215161\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Fun card. Works great with the splice cards, as well as cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Act of Treason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason\">Act of Treason</a>. Yes please, I'll take control of your <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Darksteel Colossus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Colossus\">Darksteel Colossus</a>, bash you in the face with it, and then get rid of it altogether.<br/><br/>It's also a fun reset button. Say your opponent goes first, and sacs his <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Polluted Delta\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Polluted Delta\">Polluted Delta</a> to fetch his <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Watery Grave\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Watery Grave\">Watery Grave</a> and plays it untapped to play a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ponder\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ponder\">Ponder</a>. Play your <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"mountain\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mountain\">mountain</a> and then this card. Sure, his library is a bit more organized, but he's down 3 life and a duel land.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '215161'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy69870\">SirZapdos</span>\r\n                                (12/6/2011 11:50:13 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
