    {
      "id": "PopularPost247004",
      "post_content": "This was a fun card in limited. There are a lot of combos in Kamigawa to make use of the effect. Besides [Cunning Bandit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cunning Bandit) and [Skyfire Kirin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skyfire Kirin) there's also [Blind with Anger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blind with Anger), [God's Eye, Gate to the Reikai](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=God's Eye, Gate to the Reikai) and [Akki Raider](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Akki Raider) in red. Plus it's a cheap arcane spell for all that that does in block.  \n  \nIt's not an exceptional effect since you'll usually only grab a weak creature or superfluous land, but can be fun to play around with.",
      "posted_by": "Saikuba",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost247004\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">This was a fun card in limited.  There are a lot of combos in Kamigawa to make use of the effect.  Besides <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cunning Bandit\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cunning Bandit\">Cunning Bandit</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Skyfire Kirin\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skyfire Kirin\">Skyfire Kirin</a> there's also <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blind with Anger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blind with Anger\">Blind with Anger</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"God's Eye, Gate to the Reikai\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=God's Eye, Gate to the Reikai\">God's Eye, Gate to the Reikai</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Akki Raider\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Akki Raider\">Akki Raider</a> in red.  Plus it's a cheap arcane spell for all that that does in block.<br/><br/>It's not an exceptional effect since you'll usually only grab a weak creature or superfluous land, but can be fun to play around with.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '247004'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy18183\">Saikuba</span>\r\n                        