      "post_content": "It was part of a funny combo in kamigawa constructed: with Akki Blizzard-Herder in play, then cast Crack the Earth with Desperate Ritual spliced. Then Sacrifice the akki and trigger his ability, with the three red mana left, cast stone rain. Three or two lands down in turn three.   \nThe combo is very hard to get but is really flashy.",
